definition: can/to be able to/might possibly/ability/(physics) energy

sentences.english: Can you just keep your nose out of my life?
sentences.chinese: 你能不能不要管我的生活。

sentences.english: But Peter declared, "Even if I have to die with you, I will never disown you."
sentences.chinese: 彼得说，我就是必须和你同死，也总不能不认你。

sentences.english: Beware of sale items, which make you feel like you must buy.
sentences.chinese: 当心促销品，因为它们会让你感到自己不能不买。

sentences.english: You can't be too careful when you visit the rainforest.
sentences.chinese: 因为我们要去热带雨林我们不能不特别谨严。
她能不能不要再跌落了？

sentences.english: What we do in Yenan is bound to influence the whole country.
sentences.chinese: 延安的举动，不能不影响全国。

sentences.english: China cannot not get closer to the rest of the world.
sentences.chinese: 中国不能不向世界上的其他国家靠拢。

sentences.english: We could endure anything but the absence of Internet access, " said Michael."
sentences.chinese: 密歇尔说，“我什么都能忍受，但不能不上网。”
你能不能不要再这么说了？

sentences.english: I cannot resist going up with this every night, and trying his door.
sentences.chinese: 我每天晚上总不能不带这个上楼，还要试试他的门。

sentences.english: Simplification shouldn't neglect the phrasing the and the logic regulation.
sentences.chinese: 用语求简，也不能不讲语法和逻辑。

sentences.english: Can the media stop mentioning Kim trashian in every sentence?
sentences.chinese: 媒体能不能不要每句话都提到金卡戴珊那个渣渣？

sentences.english: Will you stop following me? Who are you?
sentences.chinese: 你能不能不要再跟踪我了。你是谁呀？

sentences.english: I cannot but think of Prof.
sentences.chinese: 谈起方言，我不能不想起赵元任先生。

sentences.english: 20For we cannot help speaking about what we have seen and heard.
sentences.chinese: 我们所看见所听见的，不能不说。

sentences.english: But I have an aunt, too, who must not be longer neglected.
sentences.chinese: 可惜我也有一位舅母，再不能不回信给她了。

definition: cannot help/to be beyond control of
see 未可厚非[wei4 ke3 hou4 fei1]
in no way/not in the least/absolutely not
at a loss/unable to do anything about it/to have no choice
whatever the case/in any event/no matter what/by all possible means
